<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Huququlator</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/about.css">
</head>
<body class="main-page-body">
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <% if (loggedIn) { %>
            <!-- Logged-in view -->
            <span>Welcome, <%= username %></span>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <a href="/">Calculator</a>
                <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/upload">Upload Transactions</a>
                <a href="/filter-rules">Categorization rules</a>
                <a href="/transactions">View Transactions</a>
                <a href="/logout">Log out</a>
            </div>
        <% } else { %>
            <!-- Logged-out view -->
            <div class="navbar-left">
                <a href="/">Calculator</a>
                <a href="/about">About</a>
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-right">
                <a href="/login">Login</a>
                <a href="/register">Register</a>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <h1>About Huququlator</h1>
        <p>Huququlator is a tool designed to simplify the process of calculating Ḥuqúqu’lláh for members of the Bahá’í faith. It helps users determine their net assessable wealth, track payments, and understand the intricacies of the law.</p>

        <div class="about-section">
            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <div class="about-item" id="about1">
                <h2 onclick="toggleAbout('about1')">Our Mission</h2>
                <div class="about-content expanded">
                    <p>Huququlator aims to support members of the Bahá’í community by providing an accessible and accurate platform for fulfilling the sacred obligation of Ḥuqúqu’lláh. Our mission is to empower users to manage their financial responsibilities with clarity and confidence.</p>
                </div>
                <button class="view-more" onclick="toggleAbout('about1')">Collapse</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Section 2 -->
            <div class="about-item" id="about2">
                <h2 onclick="toggleAbout('about2')">Why Choose Huququlator?</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>Our platform is designed with simplicity and accuracy in mind. We incorporate trusted resources and expert knowledge to ensure compliance with the principles of Ḥuqúqu’lláh. With a user-friendly interface and customizable tools, Huququlator makes it easier than ever to calculate and manage your contributions.</p>
                </div>
                <button class="view-more" onclick="toggleAbout('about2')">View</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Section 3 -->
            <div class="about-item" id="about3">
                <h2 onclick="toggleAbout('about3')">Features and Benefits</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Accurate calculations based on current gold values.</li>
                        <li>Customizable transaction categories and rules.</li>
                        <li>Secure tracking of past payments and assessable wealth.</li>
                        <li>Accessible from any device with an internet connection.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <button class="view-more" onclick="toggleAbout('about3')">View</button>
            </div>

            <!-- Section 4 -->
            <div class="about-item" id="about4">
                <h2 onclick="toggleAbout('about4')">Get Involved</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>We welcome feedback and collaboration! If you’re interested in contributing to the development of Huququlator or have suggestions for improvement, please reach out to us via our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
                </div>
                <button class="view-more" onclick="toggleAbout('about4')">View</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/about.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
